omics at the graduate institute of international studies in geneva with a leading role at microsoft mr smith brings to the board broad business and international experience on a variety of issues including government affairs and public policy source netflix inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view bradford l smiths full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like bradford l smith more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in bradford l smiths network and community follow changes in bradford l smiths employment and moneyinmotion connect with bradford l smith through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example bradford l smith bradford l smiths connections  sign up now to view bradford l smiths  connections » david b wells chief financial officer netflix inc david a hyman general counsel and secretary netflix inc kirill tatarinov president chief executive officer and director citrix systems inc judith m runstad former board member wells fargo  company amy e hood executive vice president and chief financial officer microsoft corporation brian k turner board member nordstrom inc richard n barton executive chairman zillow group inc neil d hunt chief product officer netflix inc theodore a sarandos chief content officer netflix inc timothy m haley board member netflix inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla daniel a dematteo executive chairman gamestop corp david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for your interest ok browse executive pr